Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.60,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  We'll take a fifteen minute break \Nbefore we start the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:09.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, I'm heading to the fountain.  \NIf anything comes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I play against Kana-chan, \NI can move back seven lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.11,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Same when I play Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.22,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Porky and Taichi are stronger now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:28.35,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to rush myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:30.13,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll move back three lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.62,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three-syllable timing...  \NFour-syllable timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:37.38,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower pe—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:38.84,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower has...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:42.27,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The storm blasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:45.98,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}to set the Tatsuta River ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:51.65,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Timing is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.49,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you also need to have control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.07,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.76,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do I get rid of that left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:07.13,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have besides my speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:28.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If she used 1/10 of that \Nfocus on studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:31.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,her grades wouldn't be fifth \Nfrom the bottom in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.74,Chiha-title,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:49.14,Chiha-ep-title-poem-wide,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}The Cresting \NWaves\N Almost\N Look Like \NClouds in \Nthe Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:49.14,Chiha-ep-title-verse,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}Verse 20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.95,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you'll be \Nparticipating in the tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.10,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,on Sunday in Kawaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.90,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:55.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why not, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Yoshino Tournament is the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,last major tournament before \Nthe Master/Queen qualifiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be participating as-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What day is the Monday \Nfollowing the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Marine Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.23,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The first day of exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you're \Ngoing to be held back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Seriously?  For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:17.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that you are \Ndedicated to karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.47,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you need to start \Nthinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:23.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My future...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.55,East qual,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}East Qualifier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.39,queen,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.39,shinobu,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shinobu-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.97,Yoshino,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Yoshino Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.97,recently,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's recently been on her mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.97,black,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}The new \NDaddy Bear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.97,food,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Food
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.97,future,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:26.97,first,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First\N appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I found a tutor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll go over every one of your courses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with you in the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.45,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Tutor".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the verge of failing \NEnglish and Math...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.37,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Yoshino \NTournament tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.26,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.58,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino only has brackets \Nfor Class A and Class B,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.37,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we aren't going to practice today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head over to the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.68,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You placed second at Nationals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the Saitama tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you're allowed to advance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.13,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to Class A if you've \Nplaced second twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you asked the \NShiranami Society coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:16.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said that I had to \Nwin a tournament first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You too?  That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our society's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So when I told everyone I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.14,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome, Yusei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.91,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to Coach and the \Nother players at this society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.91,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.47,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me mad, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:38.35,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are the reason the old you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.86,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who hates to lose, is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.47,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can only advance if I win, \Nso that's what I'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.78,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.80,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants to play in this \Nyear's Eastern qualifier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.95,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants to make Class A this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.15,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is his last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to try to learn anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.69,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So memorize!  Memorize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Treat this like a match \Nand memorize hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:16.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll forget it \Nall before the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.09,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made it past the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.51,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a roll today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.26,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.43,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the next round,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.66,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my matches will be in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.74,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as the Class A matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.87,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.66,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're winning games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Dr. Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm winning, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.47,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing the best karuta I can, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Class A players all participate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the Yoshino Tournament to \Nprepare for the Master Qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are players from \NKansai and Kyushu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:56.04,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's an excellent chance to see how \Nyou match up against the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.11,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's preparing for \Nthe Master qualifiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.66,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.  \NHave you run into him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:14.68,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hasn't Ayase been in the restroom a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Number two.  \NThat or she fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot to put my phone on vibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.71,cellphone,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tutor.\NI'm going to cheer for Taichi. \N-Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.10,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Harada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:55.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ages since the last \Ntime you came to Kanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My knees have been killing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.45,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I had to come along
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,since so many of our \Nplayers are participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.81,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kuriyama and Dr. Harada
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get those knees patched up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.57,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,have been rivals since they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so you can play karuta again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.84,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kuriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need to watch our health.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.06,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's the director of the Nagumo Society, \Nwhere I'm registered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.53,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The third round for Class A \Nand Class B will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please move to your assigned seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:23.88,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would be in the \NClass A tournament today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:41.23,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pass that on to Chihaya,\N if she needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.94,handwriting,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.07,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.53,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata... is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:04.67,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.23,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:11.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:12.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.68,cellphone3,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that you're running \Naway from your responsibilities.\N-From your tutor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.68,cellphone2,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.75,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's so calm when he's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.22,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.66,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting nowhere with \Nstudying or karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.52,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:45.65,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, what if Taichi is all \Nalone when he wins or loses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.54,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.35,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.31,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well?  Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What round is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:21.89,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.37,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata is playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:28.98,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for there is no one else out here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.13,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:48.08,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I wait for someone \Nwho will never come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.65,Chiha-note,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:10:01.99,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my body burns like the seaweed \Ndrying on the shores of Matsuho
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.66,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.09,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.34,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won my game by 11 cards to \Nmake it to the semifinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.51,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.27,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.96,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I must hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.66,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would the mountain cherry blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.06,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the misty bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.56,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When winds send waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.44,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.62,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Arata's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.53,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.54,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It happened, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.75,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's going to come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.31,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so we have to become stronger \Nand wait for his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:17.85,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.72,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me didn't want to see him here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.54,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but deep down, I'm celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:32.88,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.00,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.49,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.  Really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboguchi Hiroshi-san,\N from the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.61,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One more card! \N One more card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.05,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give me "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:57.51,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.89,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.38,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"For the"!  "For the"!  "For the"!  "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.63,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense Dr. Harada behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:14.83,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,leaving a hovering mist \Nabove the trees and grass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.23,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For the cold nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.75,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.31,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got the card?  Terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.00,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that was pure luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.81,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I chose a card and moved before \NI heard the first syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.17,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he still almost got there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.68,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would have lost if either of the \Nother two cards had been read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.22,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The semifinals will \Nbegin in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.74,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san is our ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.28,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going to lose to someone who \Nhasn't played in eighteen months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.01,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you need to-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:18.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he go for that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How does he stay still when \Na dead card is read?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is his thinking process \Nfor sending cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:24.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?  How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:24.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.58,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even playing,\N and you're already fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:10.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Huh?  \NYou came, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We all wanted to cheer \Nfor the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.39,disguise,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:21.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,yet Desktomu-kun agreed \Nto help you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.35,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!  I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.35,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.82,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,go grab your fourth place award.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you ran off by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.57,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody from the Nagumo Society is left,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and we drove here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be the middle of the \Nnight when we reach Fukui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.87,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can give this to her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.17,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:45.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me decide \Nif she needs it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.87,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right away?!  Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:54.95,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:55.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't know if the two \Nof you were a couple now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:09.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually pretty \Nsensitive about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.56,Chiha-flashbackinternal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't afford to \Nwaste a single second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Read your textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.89,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not on the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.26,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Start from page 92 for Classic Lit.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:34.01,genji,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Tale of Genji\NLady Murasaki Shikibu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.20,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Lady Murasaki Shikibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:48.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to fit Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I get to meet him, \Nhe has to leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a love poem,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this poem is about a girl who\Nwas her childhood friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:07.79,card1,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Lady Murasaki Shikibu\N\NLong last we meet,\N only for me to leave hurriedly,\Nfor I could not recognize you, \Nlike the moon hidden behind the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.79,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a love poem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No swinging on the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.33,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was like water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.68,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,flowing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:28.37,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was gulping down soft water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.33,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about running off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:51.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan sent a message to \Nlet us know how Mashima did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.  \NHe lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was he depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima spends most of \Nhis time on karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.98,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but he always has the top \Ntest scores in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't, he'll have \Nto quit the karuta club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do the things \Nyou don't want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,before you can do the things \Nyou truly want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.08,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry! \N I'm going to study hard now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've mastered English already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, we close at 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lock up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.39,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyauchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.88,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that I also lost,\N but how could you lose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by 11 cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.95,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I felt so content after \Nmy match with Wataya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.72,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:05.20,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How was your match against Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:09.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hated it. \N Really hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.91,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was clearly thinking \Nthrough every move,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.46,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.97,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.73,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Suo wouldn't bat \Nan eye against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.58,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.17,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He mentioned the Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.09,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,while talking about a player in his
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.00,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,first year of high school who just made Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.89,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.67,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.27,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san is looking ahead \Nto the Master qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I should have watched them play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:46.18,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I should have watched from \Nthe very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:50.90,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.21,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:59.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You placed second in two Class B \Ntournaments this summer, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we go by the official standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're qualified to be in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This would break the \NShiranami Society rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.69,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but would you like me to promote you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to Class A so you can \Nplay in the East qualifier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan and Glasses are \Nwaiting for you in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Promote?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An empty train is passing \Nthrough platform 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.29,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Frustration will not last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.52,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can keep on going \Nwithout some measure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.88,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do that, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.68,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, I'm not so much \Nfocused on making Class A
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as I'm focused on becoming \Nsomeone who doesn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:09.62,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was nervous about \Nmeeting his old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it was worth the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:16.58,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.97,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp it all down.